## 4. Constraints

- KISS / DRY / hexagonal (CLAUDE.md).
- All test data via shared factories (CLAUDE.md test discipline).
- No `eslint-disable` without `Justification:` + `Approved-by:` (Phase 0 hard rule).
- `as Entity` casts only in `tests/helpers/` (Phase 7).
